{"tid":1741525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求海牙法院仲裁香港警暴　50 萬人聯署快將達標！！","createTime":"2019-11-20T11:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:19:18.000Z","uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"edd0c09d20190314893670e93b780d4c95f40b96","tid":1741525,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"文中練乙錚所著文章連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81-%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%96%84%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%B8%E8%AA%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2589%2599%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%2596%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=c7e74d76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2589%2599%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%2596%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F&h=e5a336c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81-%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%96%84%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%B8%E8%AA%AA/</a><br />\n<br />\n要求海牙法院仲裁香港警暴　50 萬人聯署快將達標<br />\n立場報道2019/11/20 &mdash; 11:39<br />\n<br />\n有人早前發起聯署要求海牙國際常設仲裁法院調查香港警察使用非法武力，截至今早 11 點，50 萬人聯署快將達標，只欠大約 1.5 萬個簽署。<br />\n<br />\n早在四個月前，「Reform Hong Kong Police」的帳戶在 <a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=8ccaa7f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a> 發起聯署，要求海牙常設仲裁法院（Permanent Court of Arbitration, PCA），調查香港警察使用非法武力。隨著香港警察圍堵理大校園，網民近日再次呼籲支持聯署。截至今早 11 點，距離 50 萬人聯署的目標，只欠大約 1.5 萬個簽署，勢將達標。<br />\n<br />\n11 月初，時事評論人練乙錚撰文〈五大訴求海牙仲裁　瑞士模式善意游說〉，提出向荷蘭海牙常設仲裁庭尋求仲裁，應是實踐「五大訴求」「最可行最文明」的辦法。他解釋，海牙常設仲裁庭「不是聯合國一部份，因此中國雖是成員卻無否決權」，仲裁亦無分原告與被告，「完全非對抗性」。他提出，今次運動雖然沒有大台，但團體乃至個人都可以「聯名參與並取得眾籌支持，到 PCA 要求給個說法」。<br />\n<br />\n立場原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4-50-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%BF%AB%E5%B0%87%E9%81%94%E6%A8%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2589%2599%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4-50-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=585d6083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2589%2599%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4-50-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&h=26a01799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4-50-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%BF%AB%E5%B0%87%E9%81%94%E6%A8%99/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji